            <h3>Equipment Care & Maintenance</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left:2rem;">
                <li><strong>Secateurs/loppers:</strong> Sharpen after each trip, clean with methylated spirits (biosecurity), oil pivot points</li>
                <li><strong>Pole pruner:</strong> Check rope condition, blade sharpness, extension locks</li>
                <li><strong>Tarpaulins:</strong> Shake out debris, dry before storing, repair tears</li>
                <li><strong>Bags:</strong> Paper bags – single use; hessian – wash and dry; plastic – wash and dry, check for holes</li>
                <li><strong>Scales:</strong> Calibrate annually, check battery before trip</li>
                <li><strong>GPS:</strong> Update maps, carry spare batteries</li>
